snippet.textDisplay: You can also thicken the muscles in your wrist area too. Forearm curls also called wrist curls, reverse forearm curls/reverse wrist curls, hammer wrist curls and reverse hammer wrist curls. Those will hit all four directions the wrist moves in, it works and compliments the forearm nicely and makes it look full all the way through.
